00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.893
So what exactly happens at the medical exam?

00:00:01.894 --> 00:00:03.093
You're getting a ton of questions

00:00:03.094 --> 00:00:04.485
regarding the medical exam,

00:00:04.534 --> 00:00:05.365
so in this video,

00:00:05.494 --> 00:00:07.725
I'm gonna cover which vaccines you need to have,

00:00:07.814 --> 00:00:09.645
what you should bring to your medical exam,

00:00:09.774 --> 00:00:11.005
how to find the right doctor,

00:00:11.334 --> 00:00:12.773
and what to do if you don't have access

00:00:12.774 --> 00:00:14.045
to your vaccination record.

00:00:14.357 --> 00:00:16.316
The purpose of the green card medical exam

00:00:16.317 --> 00:00:18.022
is to ensure that the foreign spouse

00:00:18.037 --> 00:00:20.476
seeking a green card has no health conditions

00:00:20.477 --> 00:00:23.116
that could make them inadmissible to the United States.

00:00:23.117 --> 00:00:24.716
Everyone applying for a green card

00:00:24.717 --> 00:00:26.942
must submit their medical exam to the USCIS.

00:00:27.397 --> 00:00:29.156
Couples sometimes think that any doctor

00:00:29.157 --> 00:00:30.342
can perform this exam.

00:00:30.760 --> 00:00:32.956
If you're applying from inside the United States,

00:00:32.983 --> 00:00:34.422
you will need to see a civil surgeon

00:00:34.423 --> 00:00:35.916
designated by the USCIS.

00:00:36.303 --> 00:00:38.676
Just Google find USCIS doctor

00:00:38.960 --> 00:00:40.900
and the first link will take you to the right place.

00:00:40.920 --> 00:00:42.820
From there, you'll find a list of doctors

00:00:43.080 --> 00:00:44.879
in your area based on your zip code.

00:00:44.880 --> 00:00:45.799
For the most part,

00:00:45.800 --> 00:00:47.100
all you need for this exam

00:00:47.240 --> 00:00:48.879
is your vaccination record and your ID.

00:00:48.880 --> 00:00:50.220
During the exam,

00:00:50.240 --> 00:00:52.700
the doctor will screen you for communicable diseases,

00:00:53.040 --> 00:00:54.380
drug abuse or addiction,

00:00:54.880 --> 00:00:56.638
physical or mental disorders associated

00:00:56.639 --> 00:00:57.900
with harmful behavior,

00:00:58.239 --> 00:00:59.918
and conditions that make it impossible

00:00:59.919 --> 00:01:01.180
for you to support yourself.

00:01:01.239 --> 00:01:03.598
Remember, if you don't have your vaccination record,

00:01:03.599 --> 00:01:05.238
the doctor will order a blood test

00:01:05.239 --> 00:01:07.318
in order to see what vaccines you're missing.

